{"about_the_game":"Add Potions: A Curious Tale to your wishlist!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/378690/extras/Wishlist_616.gif?t=1727895436\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/378690/extras/LunaCombatGif.gif?t=1727895436\" /><br><br>Use your wits to strategize conflict resolution that goes beyond pure combat-- you\u2019ll have to think on your feet and act quickly to sidestep danger and trick, charm, and scare your opponents into dropping valuable resources. <br><br>As powerful as your potions are, you\u2019ll find yourself up against monsters that can shrug off your most powerful attacks. Manage your resources carefully and use the environment and even other monsters to defeat your enemies, or you may find yourself with an empty satchel when you need your elixirs the most.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/378690/extras/SteamCraftingVideoFullPotTitleNX.gif?t=1727895436\" /><br><br>On her path to potions mastery, Luna must gather rare ingredients even before she brews her first potion. While her grandmother and friends teach her basic skills and recipes, Luna must fill her vials through experimentation and discovery. <br><br>Explore the deep crafting system as you discover new ingredients across 7 biomes to craft over 100 unique potions with different element combinations. <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/378690/extras/PuzzleGifTitle.gif?t=1727895436\" /><br><br>Solve devious puzzles and mysteries with your wits and your arsenal of mystical potions. With a little help from your grandmother (a powerful witch in her own right) and Helios, your cat familiar, you\u2019ll overcome the challenges of these enchanted lands.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/378690/extras/StoryTitle.png?t=1727895436\" /><br><br>Growing up is hard, and it\u2019s even harder when you\u2019re a witch! Encounter fairy tale and folklore characters as you guide Luna on her quest to become a potions master. With her sharp-tongued familiar at her side, Luna learns important coming-of-age lessons: Respect is earned, advice can be deceiving, and adults aren't always right.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/378690/extras/PetCatHeart.gif?t=1727895436\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Seeing Red","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/378690/140f57cea4ab8b0088c7aa58c7a798c14798f2c2.jpg"},{"name":"Squid Pro Quo","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/378690/0ccb319d4c8b4755e3855a2bc3b630696fe32af3.jpg"},{"name":"Beginner's Brew","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/378690/24fa74fdd081660d8738a6bad867a457831eb1c9.jpg"},{"name":"Sweep Speed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/378690/db1114459407fcc212a4444282bbab715bfc13fc.jpg"},{"name":"Huff and Puff","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/378690/07b6982dc399fc1156feca9254937954f15a39bc.jpg"},{"name":"Recluse Dethroned","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/378690/c5aa648a8c61397d0ab8dc2302aaea80c814f486.jpg"},{"name":"The True True","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/378690/ca8318a9177d61974a09102536a180440b4e8ac0.jpg"},{"name":"Sound of Silence","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/378690/951b76b866a90726bf7effa17d433050246e3d77.jpg"},{"name":"Eruption Interruption","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/378690/5a73164a4e71982debc37d263d62